Module mesakit.graph.core
Package com.telenav.mesakit.graph.map

Class Way

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.mesakit.graph.map.Way
All Implemented Interfaces:
Road, Iterable<Edge>
Direct Known Subclasses:
MapWay
public class Way extends Object implements Road, Iterable<Edge>
This class represents a way, but not necessarily a MapWay. It might be a shorter or longer stretch of a road involving one or more PBF ways.
Author:
songg, jonathanl (shibo)
